    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《<strong>King’s Bounty: Dark Side</strong>》是《King’s Bounty》系列中的一部独立作品，彻底颠覆了玩家熟悉的奇幻世界。你不再与黑暗对抗，而是掌控黑暗，从反派、流亡者与禁忌力量的视角体验故事。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以从三位独特的黑暗英雄中选择其一：兽人军阀、吸血鬼领主或恶魔女王。每位角色都拥有不同的起点、个人剧情与玩法风格，影响你探索世界、组建军队以及应对战斗的方式。他们的旅程将与熟悉的阵营交织——但这一次，光明势力成为你的敌人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/289520/extras/0ad29345eb06cd22c31418b666c01ec7.poster.avif?t=1770999815\" width=1170 height=518 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/289520/extras/0ad29345eb06cd22c31418b666c01ec7.webm?t=1770999815\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/289520/extras/0ad29345eb06cd22c31418b666c01ec7.mp4?t=1770999815\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索发生在一个广阔的世界中，充满敌对领土、危险生物以及道德灰暗的选择。城镇、荒野和地下城遍布任务、秘密与强力神器，鼓励你在不断变强的过程中谨慎规划并勇于冒险。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战斗延续了经典《King’s Bounty》的核心玩法，提供深度的回合制战术对战。站位、士气、单位能力与施法时机依然至关重要，而全新的黑暗主题单位、技能与法术则带来了新的战术可能性。胜利依赖于准备与明智决策，而非蛮力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/289520/extras/6c22cc2f087ad4d85e8425622caef7c5.poster.avif?t=1770999815\" width=1170 height=518 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/289520/extras/6c22cc2f087ad4d85e8425622caef7c5.webm?t=1770999815\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/289520/extras/6c22cc2f087ad4d85e8425622caef7c5.mp4?t=1770999815\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dark Side 通过新增同伴、神器以及与每位英雄黑暗起源相关的机制，进一步扩展了成长系统。随着敌人愈发强大、遭遇更加艰难，军队构建与长期规划变得尤为重要。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过转变视角并拥抱黑暗阵营，《<strong>King’s Bounty: Dark Side</strong>》在保留熟悉战术体验的同时呈现出截然不同的基调，挑战玩家重新思考策略，并从全新的角度探索《King’s Bounty》的世界。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/289520/extras/eec67dc2ca2b37b14e1ab2d2795d885a.poster.avif?t=1770999815\" width=1170 height=518 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/289520/extras/eec67dc2ca2b37b14e1ab2d2795d885a.webm?t=1770999815\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/289520/extras/eec67dc2ca2b37b14e1ab2d2795d885a.mp4?t=1770999815\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>三位黑暗英雄与独特的同伴系统。</strong> </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >扮演兽人、吸血鬼或恶魔女王——每位英雄都有专属同伴、能力、开局条件与成长路线，带来截然不同的流程体验。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>全新战斗同伴。</strong> </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >强大的战斗同伴将主动参与战斗，增加新的战术层次，并影响遭遇战的展开方式。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>全新黑暗主题单位、神器与狂怒技能。</strong> </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >统领全新部队，装备强力神器，释放专为黑暗阵营与激进打法设计的毁灭性狂怒技能。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>超过100个全新任务与15处新地点。</strong> </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >海量全新主线任务与支线内容，围绕蒂亚娜更黑暗的区域展开，带来新的挑战与奖励。探索皇家赏金猎人从未踏足的世界角落，那里充满独特敌人、秘密与全新的战术遭遇。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>以更黑暗的视角看待《King’s Bounty》世界。</strong> </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从冲突的另一侧体验故事：熟悉的阵营将成为敌人，道德选择也将呈现更阴暗的基调。</p>",
